<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lam hlatpi hna-hnawhnak thawng kha ka hna nih a theih i, Vawlei
 sualnak nih a ka kulh dih ti kha ka hngalh, Lung awtawm le tihnak nih
 khan ka lem hmanh hna seh law, An ka thial kho lai lo, Beaulah ram in.

[C1]
   Beau-lah ram chungah ka um, Ram nuambik ram tha chung ah, (chungah)
   Khi ram ah, tiput le cerh dong loin an luang ko, Dong loin manna changreu
   a um, A zungzal in ka khim ko, Beaulah ram chungah ka um caah.

[V2]
 Vawlei cung ah hin zumh lonak tilet nganpi a tho, Mi nih kan ral Satan
 kha doh awk a herh zungzal, Sihmanhseh Pathian bia ralhruang chungah ka
 um ca-ah, A ka phan kho lai lo, Beaulah ram ah.

[C2]
   Beau-lah ram chungah ka um, Ram nuambik ram tha chung ah, (chungah)
   Khi ram ah, tiput le cerh dong loin an luang ko, Dong loin manna changreu
   a um, A zungzal in ka khim ko, Beaulah ram chungah ka um caah.

[V3]
 Thlichia kha fakpi in hrang hmanhsehlaw ka tih lai lo, Pathian kut nih
 a ka huhphenh ca-ah ka him ko, Beaulah ram chungah cun tihphan awk
 zeihmanh a um lo, Zungzal in ka him ko, Beaulah ram ah.

[C3]
   Beau-lah ram chungah ka um, Ram nuambik ram tha chung ah, (chungah)
   Khi ram ah, tiput le cerh dong loin an luang ko, Dong loin manna changreu
   a um, A zungzal in ka khim ko, Beaulah ram chungah ka um caah.

[V4]
 Pathian riantuannak ka ruah tikah ka khuaruah a har, A bia kha ka
 theih tikah ka lung a lawm ngaingai, Keimah khamhnak ca i a riantuannak
 ka hmuh tikah, Lunglawm in ka um lai, Beaulah ram ah.

[C4]
   Beau-lah ram chungah ka um, Ram nuambik ram tha chung ah, (chungah)
   Khi ram ah, tiput le cerh dong loin an luang ko, Dong loin manna changreu
   a um, A zungzal in ka khim ko, Beaulah ram chungah ka um caah.</lyrics>
<title>BEAULAH RAM AH KAN UM CH430</title>
<hymn_number>430</hymn_number>
</song>